<item>
            <title>[DATAMONGO-290] Add support for count() in MongoTemplate</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/DATAMONGO-290</link>
                <project id="10701" key="DATAMONGO">Spring Data MongoDB</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Please add this to MongoTemplate to support the &lt;tt&gt;count()&lt;/tt&gt; method in Mongo (see &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.mongodb.org/display/DOCS/Advanced+Queries#AdvancedQueries-%7B%7Bcount%28%29%7D%7D&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;docs&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

